{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "16ec78cd-a5c1-468a-b697-e9371fc3ed26", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/16ec78cd-a5c1-468a-b697-e9371fc3ed26@1.pkg/1772597704238/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597705068", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/16ec78cd-a5c1-468a-b697-e9371fc3ed26@1.pkg/1772597704238/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597705068"}, "identifier": "16ec78cd-a5c1-468a-b697-e9371fc3ed26", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查 &ldquo;拥有积极的人生态度&rdquo; 知识点。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B：江梦南在听力严重障碍的困境下，凭借积极的人生态度，不断克服学习和生活中的困难，实现学业上的飞跃，体现了积极人生态度对战胜困难、实现价值的重要作用，符合知识点，B 正确；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A：&ldquo;只要有积极态度就能成功&rdquo; 表述绝对，成功受多种因素影响，积极态度是重要因素但非唯一，A 错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C：&ldquo;只有身体残疾的人才需要&rdquo; 错误，每个人在生活中都会遇到困难，都需要积极人生态度，C 错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D：&ldquo;能让所有困难迎刃而解&rdquo; 过于绝对，积极态度有助于解决困难，但不能保证所有困难都能轻易解决，D 错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">答案选 B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<di